{"type": "article", "id": 24568, "title": "看完《蝙蝠侠大战超人》，还可以去蝙蝠侠家里看看", "description": "你还能近距离地看到那辆酷炫的蝙蝠战车。", "date": "2016-03-28T15:17:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9249, "name": "谷歌街景"}, {"id": 17624, "name": "蝙蝠侠大战超人"}, {"id": 513, "name": "虚拟现实"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}], "category": 4, "author": 496370, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110732EmLMJFaHZp2qvBRQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>看完《蝙蝠侠大战超人》后如果还没过足瘾，那么现在你也可以在 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Bruce+Wayne's+Residence/@42.762321,-83.2835739,3a,75y,83h,90t/data=!3m8!1e1!3m6!1seK9_8zTeH7oAAAQvOrBWlg!2e0!3e2!6s%2F%2Fgeo0.ggpht.com%2Fcbk%3Fpanoid%3DeK9_8zTeH7oAAAQvOrBWlg%26output%3Dthumbnail%26cb_client%3Dsearch.TACTILE.gps%26thumb%3D2%26w%3D129%26h%3D106%26yaw%3D83.13063%26pitch%3D0!7i8000!8i4000!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x621ac62e50ef15c!5m1!1e3!6m1!1e1\">Google 街景里找到蝙蝠侠的家</a>游览一番了。<br></p>\n<p>Google 街景最近和华纳兄弟合作，一起为影迷们打造了真实的蝙蝠侠居所场景。不同于在电影中看到的有限角度，在街景中你将有机会 360 度全方位地参观蝙蝠侠的住所。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110730QurLTGvzqPwZc5WI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">谷歌街景中，蝙蝠侠居住地的鸟瞰图</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">从 Google 街景中可以看到，电影中老爷的湖景房位于密歇根州猎户座橡木国家公园附近，与之前所曝光的拍摄地一致，僻静且风景优美，与漫画中蝙蝠侠的角色设定非常一致。  <br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110731J5jnLUd2AmyPhV34.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">蝙蝠侠家中一层，你可以在房间里任意移动</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>不仅如此，你还可以深入“内部环境”一探究竟，近距离欣赏蝙蝠侠赴约莱克斯·卢瑟所驾驶的蝙蝠战车、电脑装置、以及实验室装备。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211073139gQVv4sHe7X8Pc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">蝙蝠侠的战车，走进可以看到更多的细节</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>只要你够仔细，还可以在家中找到蝙蝠侠的盔甲等许多细节。如果你拥有 Google Cardboard 或者其他头戴式设备，就可感受虚拟现实的游览体验。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110732fHieqXnE5wN9WrKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">蝙蝠侠家中二层，电影中也曾出现过这个场景</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/game/171331.htm\"> ithome</a></p>\n\n"}